name: Level one (Fridux)
description:
You play a white square that trys to get to the end of the only level in this game!

But I warn you, this won't be easy!

This one level also has a something to say...

This game and the sourcecode are licensed under the MIT License.

To build the game, you need the latest version of the Godot engine

from https://godotengine.org.

By the way, this is my first game, so it's not perfect! ;)
